# Large video assets (over GitHub's 100MB limit) — host elsewhere or via Git LFS
public/images/system/overview.mov
public/images/astra/overview.mov

# Untracked giant media that snuck in via wildcard adds — keep local, don't push
public/images/system/Screen Recording*
public/images/Fancode Homepage /
public/images/reputation/After .mov
public/images/reputation/Before .mov
public/images/astra/Meet - Persona Research Group*

